  "text": "Note, that for f (t ) = ct q , we have t (log f (t )) = t (log ct q ) = t · (q/t ) = q. So functions f j = c j t q j satisfy the conditions of Theorem A.1 if q j is polynomially bounded. (6)- [CITATION_1] . The running time of the algorithm is polynomial in n and 1/ε.",
